====================================================================
MAP INFO
====================================================================

Map                            :  gg_blocktacular
Game                          : Counter-Strike: Source
Game type                    : Gun Game
Recommended Players  : 10-20
Description                   : A small indoor map with multiple levels 
                                    various catwalks/bridges.  Each side is 
                                   different.

====================================================================
INSTALLATION
====================================================================

Place gg_blocktacular in your Steam\SteamApps\youremailaddress\
counter-strike source\cstrike\maps folder.
